The Defend Command
 
     The defend command is used to begin protecting a player from other
players or monsters.  When you are defending a person and he/she/it is
attacked, you automagically step in front and start taking hits.
Syntax follows:
 
defend <what>
  Start defending what.  If you are already defending what you will stop
  defending.
 
defend
  Lists what you are currently defending.
 
  
-Tyrus
 

